Job Details
We have an urgent opening for Battery Sales professionals. Only BATTERY SALES Experienced candidates need apply for this Junior/ Middle Management Level position. Following are the essential requirements- --Automotive and Industrial Battery sales background in UAE and Export Market --Having valid UAE Driving License --Technically qualified candidate preferred (But not essential) The candidates with an exposure to international export market will also be considered Please forward your CV to greatautojob@gmail.com for further discussions.
